other_tests.findings: Minimal dependent atelectasis; minimal nonspecific central bronchial wall thickening; otherwise clear lungs; gallbladder moderately distended with at least two large stones; trace pericholecystic fluid (up to 5 mm); small hiatal hernia; 13-mm right adrenal nodule compatible with adenoma; normal pancreas, spleen, adrenal glands, intra-abdominal loops of bowel; normal pelvis.
